{"tid":843461,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"Jude Tsang有新歌冇人講？","createTime":"2018-10-01T07:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T12:50:17.000Z","uid":18402,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c188963b9bd1b4ea7ac83f1dc0919b981a9ef4ae","tid":843461,"uid":18402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:22:49.000Z","msg":"On the road<br />\n作詞：朱琳    作曲：林德信 / JUDE / T-Ma<br />\n編：T-Ma<br />\n監：T-Ma / 朱琳<br />\n<br />\n春風吹一吹深宵到破曉<br />\n今天的旅途 可以揭曉<br />\n仲夏夜夢中你我再渺小<br />\n車燈閃了<br />\n車燈閃了<br />\n出發了<br />\n<br />\nCause when I'm loving you<br />\n全為你燃燒<br />\n所有錯失 固執<br />\n通通不緊要<br />\n沿路驟降塵囂<br />\n遊十里路得到你淺笑<br />\n在途上一起心跳<br />\nRiding together with you<br />\n<br />\n金色的憂鬱倒映你眼睛<br />\n灰色的鐵路 裝了嘆息<br />\n熱鬧是幻境偶爾也冷清<br />\n孤單一個<br />\n孤單一個<br />\n不清醒<br />\n<br />\n怎麼這地球在發嬲<br />\n怎麼這路途太顫抖<br />\n或者我倆未捨得放手<br />\n<br />\nCause when I'm loving you<br />\n全為你燃燒<br />\n所有錯失 固執<br />\n通通不緊要<br />\n沿路驟降塵囂<br />\n遊十里路得到你淺笑<br />\n在途上一起<br />\n<br />\n即使一起有過一些差錯<br />\n讓我跟你繼續剖析困擾<br />\n人類的可笑<br />\n傻在破裂時看天呼叫<br />\n修補得到這最愛<br />\n<br />\nCause when I'm loving you<br />\n全為你燃燒<br />\n所有錯失 固執<br />\n通通不緊要<br />\n沿路驟降塵囂<br />\n遊十里路得到你淺笑<br />\n在途上一起心跳<br />\n覓尋著彼此心跳<br />\nI'll be there for you<br />\nRiding together with you<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/jWyNgOWMP44\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjWyNgOWMP44&d=nlBVOU48iSINXS0LVaR%2FY7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=cafa4e6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jWyNgOWMP44</a>"},{"pid":"520d5fd9e4b82aba51de9ef61210da01854fd674","tid":843461,"uid":18402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:28:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  清泉"},{"pid":"642dfcf8e27951c95cd8451873073ac0941a773d","tid":843461,"uid":159140,"like":8,"dis